high_descs: Turn around, walk straight, turn right to face the stove, walk to the stove.
Grab the kettle from on top of the stove.
Turn right, walk straight, turn left to face the kitchen sink.
Place the kettle in the kitchen sink, turn on the faucet, fill the sink with water, drain the water, and pick up the kettle.
Turn right , walk to the counter, turn right, walk straight, turn left when you reach the waste basket, walk straight to the window, turn right to the table.
Place the kettle on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean kettle on top of the table.

high_descs: turn around and walk forwards a bit, then turn right and walk over to the kitchen stove
grab the tea kettle off of the back left burner on the stove
turn right and walk until your reach the sink on your left, turn to face the sink
fill the tea kettle with water, and pick it up again
turn right and walk to the end of the kitchen counter, then turn right and walk to the fridge, then hang a left and walk to the end of the room, then a right and walk to the table
place the tea kettle down on the table
anns.task_desc: place a tea kettle with water in it on top of the kitchen table

high_descs: Turn left and walk over to the stove
Pick up the tea kettle from the stove
Turn right and walk to the kitchen sink
Rinse the tea kettle under water in the sink and then remove it
Turn right and walk over to the far side of the round dining table by the corner
Put the kettle on the table left of the clear bowl
anns.task_desc: Put the cleaned tea kettle on the dining table
